  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Preoperative anxiety of patients who will undergo septorhinoplasty surgery will be measured&#xD;
      and their hemodynamic parameters will be recorded afterwards. Then, a video will be shown to&#xD;
      the patients through virtual reality glasses and the effect of this application on their&#xD;
      anxiety will be investigated.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
